		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>ok im going to skip the arguements and go with a recommended solution here:</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Currently MB caps at 9500ish, needing 1.2 to 1 ratio to do that.&nbsp; prior to the changes it was 1 to 2 to 1?&nbsp; I seem to remember something about it being 1 to 4 to 1 but im not sure.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>if we go with a hard cap of 3k mana at 59, and a max 2.5 to 1, then we are at 7.5k damage. (same as CH, image that?)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>if we then use ratio of growth at the oppropriate levels:</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>level 62, hard cap of 3k, and 3 to 1.... 9k total damage.</DIV>
<DIV>level 65, hard cap of 2.5k, and&nbsp;3.8 to 1.... 9.5k total damage.</DIV>
<DIV>level 68, hard cap of 2k, and&nbsp;5 to 1.... 10k total damage.</DIV>
<DIV>level 70, hard cap of 1k, and 10 to 1.... 10k total damage.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>that way we get some of both good suggestions, and the damage does not scale away so much as to need the 1 minute rule.</DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							<A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=411608">Hurk</a><br>~~~~~<br>"Character is always lost when a high ideal is sacrificed on the altar of conformity and popularity." - Anon<br><br>"You can tell the character of someone by how they treat those that can do nothing for them." -Hendrix
							</div>
								
		</td></tr>
		<tr>
		
