<P>15k is the max&nbsp;damage that you'd be doing on a crit with a 3k cap on the mana spent based on a 2.5 to 1 damage-to-mana ratio.&nbsp; A 3k mana cap is what we're working with in these discussions&nbsp;for the level 59 ability.</P>
