			<DIV></DIV>
<DIV>Hmmm, as some have suggested, I think maybe splitting MB into 2 different abilities might be a good idea.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>1) Change&nbsp;MANABURN &nbsp;to a level 69 ability that takes our entire manapool but does 30% of a mobs <EM>remaining</EM> HPS guaranteed. no stacking timer, unresistable.&nbsp;(that way, multiple wizards can use but never kill a raid boss on their own because it's 30% of an ever diminishing amt, would be most useful to pop this one off at the beginning of an encounter, with diminihing returns the further into an encounter th raid gets, preventing trivialization) ...refresh, 2.5 hrs...&nbsp; Add&nbsp;Improved MB AA&nbsp; to lower amt of manapool used to 90% / 80% / 70% / 60% / 50%. ..3 aa per rank?</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>2)&nbsp; add a new ability at level 59 to replace MB, call it Devastate.&nbsp; use your manafree nuke option #2 and add subsequent AAs later to scale it up appropriately.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
